pendences of the effect which we are discussing might\npermit to separate it. Detection of this signal using future narrow-band\nspectral observations can give information about the details of how the cosmic\nrecombination proceeds, and how Silk damping operates during recombination.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Feb 2005 12:22:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 May 2005 15:20:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-10"}
